markets.title: How many Deputy Secretaries of the Cabinet will be confirmed before May 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If exactly 3 Deputy Cabinet Secretaries are confirmed by the Senate before May 1, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Only the first successful confirmation for each position will be included. The relevant positions eligible are: The State Department's Deputy Secretary of State and Deputy Secretary of State for Management and Resources, The Deputy Secretary of the Treasury, The Deputy Secretary of Defense, The Deputy Attorney General, The Deputy Secretary of the Interior, The Deputy Secretary of Agriculture, The Deputy Secretary of Commerce, The Deputy Secretary of Labor, The Deputy Secretary of Health and Human Services, The Deputy Secretary of Housing and Urban Development, The Deputy Secretary of Transportation, The Deputy Secretary of Energy, The Deputy Secretary of Education, The Deputy Secretary of Veterans Affairs, and The Deputy Secretary of Homeland Security.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
